column4: but i do not want to format or partition my disk because of possible data loss!
ive never format or partition before
and i have lots of sensitive data
then back up all of your data
i'd suggest finding one beforehand then. if this data is that sensitive it NEEDS to be backed up
if it's company data i'd back it up regardless of how unimportant it may be
how much data is it you want to keep?

ok look seriously. Wubi is not really going to help you. My best and only suggestion to you is to spend a few bucks to invest in a second hard drive to back up your data. Once you've done that I'd be willing to help you more.
until you can lose the caps and get a better attitude, people aren't going to be very helpful to you
